AllTitles: Ramen Aka Neko|Red Cat Ramen|ラーメン赤猫
Description:
Meet Tamako, who's found her way into an interview at a ramen shop run solely by cats. When the feline manager asks if she likes cats, Tamako admits that she's actually more of a dog person...only to be hired on the spot! But her job description isn't quite what she expects ? rather than serving ramen, she's now a dedicated cat caretaker...?!
Source: Manga Plus

AllTitles: Tasogare Outfocus|Twilight Out of Focus|Tasogare Out Focus|黄昏アウトフォーカス
Description:
Film enthusiast http://anidb.net/ch133525 [Tsuchiya Mao] and his lone wolf roommate http://anidb.net/ch133526 [Ootomo Hisashi] make three promises:
① That Mao will never tell anyone that Hisashi is gay and has a boyfriend,
② That Hisashi will never approach Mao "in that way," and
③ That they'll respect each other's "private time."
The second-years' ground rules should ensure a peaceful life together in their dorm, but reality is never as simple as it seems in the movies, and some things are not so easily promised...
Source: Kodansha

Description:
* Based on a romance manga by http://anidb.net/cr71268 [Pom].
Can true love really overcome any obstacles? http://anidb.net/ch138102 [Saki], a high school student, confesses her feelings to http://anidb.net/ch138101 [Makoto]. Taken aback, Makoto reveals his secret, but the sudden discovery doesn't seem to bother Saki who is already head over heels for him. After being rejected, Saki asks http://anidb.net/ch138100 [Ryuuji], Makoto's childhood friend, for some advice on how to win his heart. A love triangle unfolds when Ryuuji realizes that he might also have some feelings for his old friend.
Source: Webtoons

MainTitle: Ore wa Subete o "Parry" Suru: Gyaku Kanchigai no Sekai Saikyou wa Boukensha no Yume o Miru
AllTitles: Ore wa Subete o "Parry" Suru: Gyaku Kanchigai no Sekai Saikyou wa Boukensha no Yume o Miru|I Parry Everything: What Do You Mean I'm the Strongest? I'm Not Even an Adventurer Yet!|I Parry Everything!|俺は全てを【パリイ】する ~逆勘違いの世界最強は冒険者の夢をみる~|I Parry Everything to Become the Greatest Adventure!
Description:
The Kingdom of Clays faces a dire crisis: an assassination attempt has just been made on its own http://anidb.net/ch139454 [Princess Lynneburg], and its neighboring countries eye the aftermath like starving vultures, plotting the Kingdom's downfall. The ensuing conflict will shape the face of the continent for centuries to come...but http://anidb.net/ch139452 [Noor] doesn't have a clue about any of that! Having freshly arrived at the royal capital after over a decade of rigorous, isolated training at his mountain home, he's dead set on achieving his childhood dream of becoming an adventurer, even if the only skills he possesses are useless ones. Sure, he can [Parry] thousands of swords in the span of a single breath, but everybody knows you need more than that if you want to be an adventurer! Our hero's road to making his dream come true will be long(?) and arduous(?)—but if there's one thing Noor's not afraid of, it's some good ol' fashioned hard work!

* Based on a romantic cosplay comedy manga by http://anidb.net/cr69711 [Hashimoto Yuu].
"I have no interest in real girls!" So claims http://anidb.net/ch134498 [Okumura], the president of the school's manga club. He's your typical otaku, obsessed with a sexy (fictional) 2D manga character known as Liliel. Then the new school year starts, and a (real!) 3D girl named http://anidb.net/ch134497 [Ririsa] whose passion is cosplay joins the club. Description:
* Based on a fantasy isekai light novel series written by http://anidb.net/cr75215 [Shinozaki Kaoru] and illustrated by http://anidb.net/cr75216 [KWKM].
Abruptly catapulted into a fantasy world, http://anidb.net/ch140332 [Mimori Touka] and his classmates have been summoned by the world's resident http://anidb.net/ch140331 [Goddess] to serve as heroes. Luckily, most of the students display amazing skills upon arrival—except for Mimori, whose abilities bottom out at a measly E-rank. With no further use for him, the Goddess banishes Mimori to a dungeon from which no one has ever returned alive. Yet, as it turns out, Mimori's skills aren't so much worthless as they are abnormal. Abnormally powerful, even. If Mimori can only claw his way back to the surface, nothing will stand in his way from getting revenge.

AllTitles: Tensui no Sakuna-hime|Sakuna: Of Rice and Ruin|天穂のサクナヒメ
Description:
* Based on an action role-playing simulation video game developed by http://anidb.net/cr75730 [Edelweiss].
Long ago, the spoiled http://anidb.net/ch139003 [Princess Sakuna] enjoyed a life of leisure in the Mihashira Capital among the gods and spirits of Yanato. But on the floating bridge of heaven separating the immortal Lofty Realm from the Lowly Realm of mortals, a chance encounter with the children of men (or, as they call themselves, the humans) led to a series of mishaps.
Alas, this culminated in their banishment to Hinoe Island, the so-called Isle of Demons. The ruling deity, http://anidb.net/ch139001 [Lady Kamuhitsuki], charged Sakuna with securing a foothold for the capital and rooting out the hordes of demonic beasts that plague the island. And, of course, as a goddess she must also look after the wayward children of men who were alongside her.  But even a goddess needs to eat, and so the tale of rice and ruin begins...

AllTitles: Kono Sekai wa Fukanzen Sugiru|この世界は不完全すぎる|Quality Assurance in Another World
Description:
* Based on an adventure fantasy manga by http://anidb.net/cr71256 [Satou Masamichi].
http://anidb.net/ch131298 [Nikola] is just a village girl working at the inn...until the day dragons invade, and she meets http://anidb.net/ch131299 [Haga], a scholar of everything around him. He's a part of an elite society called "Seeker," created to address a series of maladies plaguing their usually peaceful world. But both Nikola and Haga have secrets they hide...ones that will change each other's very existence...

AllTags: shounen|dynamic|target audience|themes|source material|setting|elements|place|fictional location|novel|virtual world|fantasy|strong male lead|origin|cast|isekai|speculative fiction|Japanese production
Description:
THE NEW GATE—an online game transformed into a life-and-death struggle for its players. Thanks to the valiant efforts of http://anidb.net/ch136157 [Shin], the most powerful of them all, an end to the game and freedom for everyone seemed within reach. But just moments after Shin defeats the game's final boss, he finds himself bathed in an unknown light and transported some 500 years into the future of the in-game world. Thrown from a simple game gone wrong into a strange new land, one young swordsman of unrivalled strength is about to embark on a legendary journey!
Source: One Peace Books

MainTitle: Sasayaku You ni Koi o Utau
AllTitles: Sasayaku You ni Koi o Utau|Sasayaku You ni Koi wo Utau|sasakoi|ささやくように恋を唄う|Whisper Me a Love Song
Description:
* Based on a yuri manga by http://anidb.net/cr58820 [Takeshima Eku].
Bubbly, energetic first-year high school student http://anidb.net/ch129688 [Himari] falls head over heels for her senpai http://anidb.net/ch129687 [Yori] after hearing her band perform on the first day of school. Himari tells Yori she just loves her, and, to Himari's surprise, Yori says she loves Himari back! But when Himari realizes that she and her senpai are feeling two different kinds of love, she begins to ask herself what "love" really means...
Source: Kodansha

AllTitles: Fanpai Chushihua|Villain Initialization|反派初始化
Description:
In 2048, the super villain Ling Chen (alias Penrose) accidentally traveled back to the sophomore year of high school in 2030 during a fierce battle with his arch-enemy superhero Ye Zi Mu. After returning home to see his aunt and confirming the fact that he had traveled through time, Ling Chen decided that this time he must protect his aunt who was killed by Ye Zimu in his previous life and get rid of Ye Zimu. The timeline of "rebirth" is full of variables. This time, Ling Chen believes that he can change everything!

AllTitles: Yong Sheng: Qizhuang Shanhe|Immortality 3|Yong Sheng 3rd Season|永生 气壮山河
Description:
In the majestic fantasy world, how does the protagonist Fang Han traverse the world with his own power? Relying on a stubbornness that refused to admit defeat, he broke through the mystery of supernatural powers and forged his physical body into an immortal body. Endless novel magic weapons, a new prosperous world of immortals, demons and mortals will be opened by the protagonist one by one. It will take you to experience the fantasy style of immortals, demons, humans, demons and gods, and kings and emperors. The protagonist will also experience love, hatred, entanglements, and battles between immortals and demons in the world. Finally, we will lead you on the road to the top.

AllTitles: Jueshi Zhan Hun|Peerless Battle Spirit|绝世战魂
Description:
The Xuanling Sect, the head of the four major sects, came to Shuicheng to select disciples for the first time in many years. The Fang and Qin families started fighting openly and secretly around this opportunity that would determine their fate. In the end, Qin Nan relied on his dedicated training, excellent talent, and the God of War Soul obtained by chance, and under the fair judgment of the messenger Xiao Qingxue, he successfully reversed the decline and defeated the Fang family. After entering the sect, Qin Nan aroused the hatred of Ouyang Jun, the son of the sect leader, because of his involvement in Xiao Qingxue's forced marriage. In order to continue to become stronger and repay Xiao Qingxue's kindness, Qin Nan repeatedly defeated powerful enemies, won the first place in the Wanxiang Competition and the Outer Sect Competition, entered the Wuyuan Pavilion with the four major sect geniuses, and obtained the power to stir up the continent. A shocking secret, an appointment with Leng Feng to fight in the Palace of Life and Death, overcoming the siege of Linshui City by the Beihai family, exploring the Nine-Character Mantra Tower, and vowing to fight the evil forces of the sect to the end.

AllTitles: Xiaobing Chuanqi|Legend of Soldier|小兵传奇
Description:
It is adapted from "The Legend of Xiaobing". Interstellar wars have lasted for hundreds of years, with various civilizations fighting against each other. Tang Long, who cherishes the dream of a marshal, used his wisdom to stop the Silver Eagle Empire's plan to provoke a black hole bomb war. He got acquainted with the Federation Central Computer Star Zero, experienced brutal training from mechanical instructors, rescued the self-propelled gunboat team, and led a company of female soldiers to re-enter the war. He was freed, but little did he know that what was waiting for him was a bigger conspiracy of the enemy...

AllTitles: Hui Ming: Fenghuo San Yue|Back to the Great Ming|Reincarnated Marquis|回铭之烽火三月
Description:
High school student Zheng Shaopeng fell asleep in a history class. When he woke up, he found that he had arrived at the Danzhu Dynasty in the history book and transformed into the poor scholar Yang Lin. At first, Yang Lin could not adapt to ancient life, but as he used modern thinking to develop some small inventions, Yang Lin became popular and loved by the villagers, and he gradually found his own sense of belonging. In an era of internal and external troubles, Yang Lin experienced wars and witnessed the sufferings of the people. He relied on his wisdom and ability to win a place in the court, and gradually led the Danzhu Dynasty to curb corrupt officials internally and defend against powerful enemies externally. With scientific and technological progress, The road to a powerful nation by breaking through superstition.

Description:
"The Storm" tells the story of top warriors Bu Jingyun and Nie Feng. In order to cope with a catastrophe that was about to sweep the entire world, they transformed into quantum states with the help of unknown seniors and mysterious extraterrestrial visitors, and their whereabouts are unknown. Three thousand years later, an asteroid hit the earth, turning the surface into a barbaric wasteland. Human beings trapped underground gradually discovered that there is a super power known as "pulse energy" in the human body. Bu Tianyun, an orphan from Dungeon 32, accidentally awakened Bu Jingyun who was sleeping in the meteorite. From then on, he discovered the "pulse energy" potential in his body, and together with Nie Feng's successor Nie Zifeng, embarked on the journey to become " The journey of training as a "pulse warrior", fighting to protect the world.

AllTitles: Xiehou Ta de Shaonu Shidai|Mom, I'm Sorry|邂逅她的少女时代
Description:
In order to save his terminally ill mother, the unfilial son Dong Cuican signed a "contract" with a mysterious man, exchanging his own time for his dying mother. After recovery, his mother Yan Jinyu not only returned to her healthy state at the age of 20, but also relied on her maturity and optimism that surpassed her "peers" to live a more wonderful life that she had never dared to imagine. However, on the other hand, in order not to worry his mother, Dong Cuican concealed the truth about his life and shouldered the cost of the contract alone. And decided to make up for his past regrets and repay his mother's kindness in the last time of his life...

AllTags: shounen|alien|cross-dressing|target audience|themes|fetishes|source material|setting|elements|time|place|calling your attacks|super power|past|Earth|historical|Japan|humanoid alien|love polygon|manga|Asia|action|science fiction|fantasy|comedy|romance|school life|unsorted|damsel in distress|1960s|running gag|origin|speculative fiction|Japanese production
Description:
It is Tokyo, 1969. Earth is under the attack of the Invaders. Fortunately, though, the public is unaware of this. But to the secret organization, A.E.G.I.S., the threat is very real, and it is up them to stop this invasion. One day on his route to high school, Ukiya Shun observes a battle between a young girl and a group of Invaders. He ends up helping her and discovers that much like the girl, he possesses the ability to generate a gate of special power that only a few other people are gifted with. As a result, Ukiya then joins A.E.G.I.S. in an effort to recruit other Gate Keepers in order to protect the city, all while doing his best not to imitate his late father, whom he despises.
Source: ANN

AllTitles: Inazuma Eleven GO: Galaxy|Inazuma Eleven GO 3|inago3|イナズマイレブンGO ギャラクシー|Inazuma Eleven Go (2013)|Inazuma Eleven GO: Galaxy|闪电十一人GO 银河
Description:
Soccer has come back after winning their fight against the Second Stage Children and Raimon Eleven returned to their own time. The soccer ban has been lifted and everyone can enjoy soccer freely again. But this marks the beginning of a new challenge for http://anidb.net/ch31137 [Tenma] and his friends!
Football Frontier International V2, a tournament to determine the best players of the world, is about to commence. On the day the Japanese representatives are to be picked, aiming to win the title of world champions, over 100 candidates including Tenma and the Raimon Eleven are summoned and admits all the excitement, the appointed coach http://anidb.net/ch68427 [Ryuusei Kuroiwa] announces the new members for Shinsei Inazuma Japan! Among the members are... Tenma, http://anidb.net/ch31142 [Tsurugi] and http://anidb.net/ch31138 [Shindou], but the other 8 are unknown players that no one has ever seen or heard of. This wasn't the only surprising thing! That is, none of these 8 have every played soccer before...
The reason for their selection is shrouded in mystery. What is Kuroiwa hoping to achieve!? And what is the hidden truth behind the construction of Shinsei Inazuma Japan!?
The curtain raises as Tenma leads Japans most novice group of amateurs into the fierce battle to earn the title of the world's bests!

AllTags: seinen|target audience|themes|source material|elements|contemporary fantasy|manga|fantasy|horror|black and white|curse|technical aspects|origin|speculative fiction|Japanese production
Description:
* Based on a seinen supernatural horror manga series by http://anidb.net/cr24045 [Itou Junji].
Kurouzu-chou, a small fogbound town on the coast of Japan, is cursed. According to Saitou Shuuichi, the withdrawn boyfriend of teenager Goshima Kirie, their town is haunted not by a person or being but by a pattern: uzumaki, the spiral, the hypnotic secret shape of the world. It manifests itself in small ways: seashells, ferns, whirlpools in water, whirlwinds in air. And in large ways: the spiral marks on people's bodies, the insane obsessions of Shuuichi's father, the voice from the cochlea in your inner ear. As the madness spreads, the inhabitants of Kurouzu-chou are pulled ever deeper, as if into a whirlpool from which there is no return...
Source: VIZ

Hyper girl http://anidb.net/ch6108 [Edomae Azuki] and her friends http://anidb.net/ch6109 [Matsuki Mutsumi] and http://anidb.net/ch6110 [Shihoudou Serika] protect the peaceful order of a town by transforming into Kigurumikku-Swan, Kigurumikku-Falcon, and Kigurumikku-Swallow, respectively, via cosplay outfits. Description:
Robot bugs suddenly attack Tokyo and robot gamer Ryusei is given a real, mechanical robot trooper to see whether he is a qualified fighter in a war which he has just now become a part of. Amazingly the controls to the personal trooper are just as in the game.

Description:
* Based on the Super Robot Taisen series of tactical role-playing video games.
The story takes place half a year after the end of Divine Wars which had Earth's government facing off against the rebel Divine Crusaders and alien Aerogators.
As the struggle continues against Divine Crusader remnants, a new alien menace draws near.
~ translated and adapted from official site by Cranston

Description:
http://anidb.net/ch2069 [Kurosaki Ichigo] is a teenager gifted with the ability to see spirits. His life is drastically changed by the sudden appearance of a Shinigami (literally, Death god) - one who governs the flow of souls between the human world and the afterlife - named http://anidb.net/ch3720 [Kuchiki Rukia], who arrives in search of a Hollow, a dangerous lost soul. When Rukia is severely wounded while trying to defeat the Hollow, she attempts to transfer half of her Reiatsu (literally, Spiritual pressure) energy to Ichigo so that he can defeat the Hollow. However, Ichigo takes almost all of her energy, transforming into a Shinigami and allowing him to defeat the Hollow with ease. With her powers diminished, Rukia is left stranded in the human world until she can recover her strength. In the meantime, Ichigo must take over Rukia's role as a Shinigami, battling Hollows and guiding souls to the afterlife realm known as the Soul Society.
Source: Wikipedia

Description:
* Based on an action fantasy one-shot manga by http://anidb.net/cr979 [Kubo Taito].
In this world there is a "FRONT" side and a "REVERSE" side.
Historically 72% of all the deaths in London are related to dragons, fantastical beings invisible to the majority of the people. While unknown to most, some people have been standing up to these dragons. Only inhabitants of Reverse London who live in the hidden "reverse" side of London can see the dragons. Even then, only a selected few become qualified enough as witches or wizards to make direct contact with them.
The protagonists of the story are witch duo http://anidb.net/ch108786 [Niihashi Noel] and http://anidb.net/ch108785 [Ninny Spangcole]. They are protection agents for Wing Bind (WB), an organization for dragon conservation and management. Their mission is to protect and manage the dragons within London on behalf of the people.
Source: Official website

Description:
In Karakura Town, there has been a sudden outbreak of unidentifiable spirits called blanks (vacant souls) while in the skies of Soul Society, the real world has been reflected. A mysterious female shinigami called http://anidb.net/ch7207 [Senna] has appeared before http://anidb.net/ch2069 [Ichigo] along with a man named http://anidb.net/ch10096 [Ganryuu], leading a group called the Dark Ones.
Source: ANN

Description: When an artifact known as the "King's Seal" is stolen during transport from Soul Society, http://anidb.net/ch8354 [Hitsugaya Toushirou] is assigned to retrieve it. Toushirou goes missing after a battle with the thieves, leading Seireitei to suspect him of treachery. They order his immediate capture and execution. Unwilling to believe him capable of such a crime, Ichigo, Rangiku, Rukia, and Renji set out to find Toushirou and clear his name. Meanwhile, Toushirou is still searching for the thieves, and stumbles upon a dark secret involving a shinigami long since dead.

Description: A mysterious reiatsu (spiritual particle) explosion occurs in the center of Seireitei in Soul Society, causing it to be destroyed. At the exact same time, a major change overwhelms http://anidb.net/ch3720 [Kuchiki Rukia], which leaves her losing something important inside. Urahara Kisuke sends http://anidb.net/ch2069 [Kurosaki Ichigo] to Soul Society to investigate the disturbance. Upon reaching Seireitei, Ichigo is set upon and attacked by shinigamis, once allies, who have no memory of him and Rukia. Description:
"Hell" is the place where a person is sent to who committed violent crimes when they were alive. Shinigami are forbidden to go there. One day prisoners revolt and make their escape to Karakura - the real world - where http://anidb.net/ch2069 [Ichigo] and his friends live in. Ichigo and his friends are defeated one after the other by prisoners with overwhelming power. A mysterious man appears who comes to their rescue. With http://anidb.net/ch36163 [Kokutou] leading the way Ichigo, http://anidb.net/ch3720 [Rukia], http://anidb.net/ch3723 [Uryuu], and http://anidb.net/ch8722 [Renji] marches into Hell to save the world.
Note: Episode 299 of http://anidb.net/a2369 [Bleach] serves as a prologue to this movie.

Description:
* A standalone story set in the same universe as Cyberpunk 2077, an open-world, action-adventure game from CD PROJEKT RED.
A street kid is trying to survive in a technology and body modification-obsessed city of the future. Having everything to lose, he chooses to stay alive by becoming an edgerunner—a mercenary outlaw also known as a cyberpunk.
Source: cyberpunk.net

Description:
* Based on a comedy slice of life manga by http://anidb.net/creator/63803 [Oda Tomohito].
http://anidb.net/ch117224 [Komi] is the most popular girl at Itan Private High School. People are awestruck by her beauty, grace, and stoicism. But after homeroom introductions, http://anidb.net/ch117225 [Tadano] discovers that Komi isn't withdrawn because of her esteemed popularity. It's because she possesses extreme social anxiety and has trouble communicating with others. After managing to exchange words via chalkboard, Komi reveals that it's her dream to make one hundred friends. Tadano becomes the first and promises to help with the other ninety-nine.
Source: ANN

Description:
When young adventurer http://anidb.net/ch132540 [Laios] and his company are attacked and soundly thrashed by a dragon deep in a dungeon, the party loses all its money and provisions...and a member! They're eager to go back and save her, but there is just one problem: If they set out with no food or coin to speak of, they're sure to starve on the way! But Laios comes up with a brilliant idea: "Let's eat the monsters!" Slimes, basilisks, and even dragons...none are safe from the appetites of these dungeon-crawling gourmands!
Source: Yen Press
Note: The first three episodes received a three-week advance screening run in Japan starting on December 8, 2023. Also, the first episode was screened at AnimagiC Mannheim in Germany on August 5, 2023. The regular broadcast started on January 4, 2024.

MainTitle: Dungeon Meshi: Senshi no Kantan Cooking!
AllTitles: Dungeon Meshi: Senshi no Kantan Cooking!|ダンジョン飯~センシのかんたんクッキング!~
AllTags: cooking|themes|source material|manga|stop motion|commercial|live-action imagery|technical aspects|origin|Japanese production
Description:
A stop-motion short of Dungeon Meshi commissioned by Kadokawa in honor of the 5th tankoubon going on sale. It features Senshi's hands trying to prepare a walking mushroom. It is the same walking mushroom as shown in the manga's 1st volume in the "Monster Tidbits" bonus chapter.

Description:
The Deep Sleep Capsule technology has allowed man to reach out to the stars. These chambers slow the ageing process by 95%, so that a 20-year trip passes, and the traveller only ages by one year.
The year is 2264, and the Syncam Corporation has sent the Saldes and its crew of 13 and one cat out into deep space to explore the potential of a newly found planet 20 years away. Soon after the crew awakens from stasis, however, ever more threatening problems mount up: first, the crew learns that two of the crew are not who they claim to be; then, one by one, crew members die suddenly; and finally the ship begins to turn against them. But this is not the end of their troubles...
What was supposed to be a simple exploratory mission has become a struggle for survival...
- The film is heavily inspired by Ridley Scott's Alien and by John Carpenter's The Thing.
Source: AnimeNfo

Description:
Roots Search is the story of a psychic research facility that becomes a stopover point for a spaceship full of dead people. Of course there was a bad thing on the ship that killed everybody, and now it's going to hunt down the few people on the space station.
- The plot and setting bears a lot of similarities to the 1979 film Alien, of which it is loosely based on.
Source: Akemi's Anime World

The Demon Lord has been defeated by a brave warrior, but is destined to arise again! Ten years later, http://anidb.net/ch123010 [he] emerges early from his slumber to exact his revenge. However, he returns to find that neither the world nor the legendary http://anidb.net/ch123009 [hero] are what they once were. Can the powers of darkness triumph over...a shut-in slob?
Source: Seven Seas Entertainment
Note: The first episode received an advance release on Kadokawa's YouTube channel on June 24, 2023. The regular TV broadcast started on July 3, 2023.

Description:
* Based on a manga written and illustrated by http://anidb.net/cr38832 [Oshikiri Rensuke], serialised in Gekkan Big Gangan.
1991. The year of the Gulf War. The year Mount Unzen erupted. The year the Ten-Day War in Slovenia broke out. The year the world wavered.
http://anidb.net/ch96703 [Yaguchi Haruo], a 6th grader, is not only the least popular in his school, but also has the worst grades, a bad attitude towards others, and cannot be called attractive either. The only thing he lives for are video games, and this happens to be the only thing he is really good at. Until one day, he plays Street Fighter II against http://anidb.net/ch96694 [Oono Akira], a well-off female classmate, who proves to him that she is not only more popular, intelligent, attractive, and lucky than he is, but also... better than him at playing video games!
Haruo's small world wavers...
Source: Batoto
Note: Due to a then-ongoing legal dispute concerning http://anidb.net/cr1225 [SNK Playmore]'s intellectual property, the manga's publisher http://anidb.net/cr1130 [Square Enix] voluntarily recalled its volumes from the stores, also suspending serialization, further publication and digital sales of volumes, and development of the anime adaptation. The two companies eventually settled out of court and Square Enix resumed the previously halted activities.

Description:
The final summer of middle school, Shotaro Futaba discovers boys gymnastics and is completely enamored by it. Shotaro ends up going to Soshukan Private High School (aka Ao High) and decides to visit the boys gymnastics club. He's greeted by very unique senpais and a star gymnast named Misato Ryoya. Dedicating your life to something you love during your fiery days of youth... Of course, there is frustration, and fights, but see how these boys work together as a team towards a similar goal in this drama about sports and youth.
Source: crunchyroll

AllTitles: Rising Impact|ライジングインパクト|Rising Impact
Description:
http://anidb.net/ch136595 [Nanaumi Gawain] is a third-grader with an incredible love for baseball and making the ball really fly. In a chance encounter with a female professional golfer, http://anidb.net/ch136600 [Nishino Kiria], he learns that golf will allow him to hit a ball further than any other sport.
Using his physical strength and keen observational skills gained from living in a rural mountain area, he manages to hit the ball to such an impressive distance that it rivals even that of professionals. With Kiria's help, the new golf enthusiast enrolls at Camelot Academy, a prestigious school for both skilled and aspiring golfers from around the world. Gawain wants to be the best professional golfer in the world but there are other golf prodigies with extraordinary skills that stand in his way and he has to face various trials to overcome them.

In the Edo period, there was a shrine maiden called "Itsukihime" in the mountain village of Kadono. http://anidb.net/ch138426 [Jinta], a young man who acts as the shrine maiden's guardian despite being a stranger, encounters a mysterious demon who speaks of the far future in the forest where he went to defeat it. MainTitle: Boku no Tsuma wa Kanjou ga Nai
AllTitles: Boku no Tsuma wa Kanjou ga Nai|My Wife Has No Emotion|僕の妻は感情がない
Description:
* Based on a romantic manga by http://anidb.net/cr75686 [Sugiura Jirou].
http://anidb.net/ch138702 [Takuma] is a single guy who does nothing but go to work and come home. Too tired to do chores, he decides to get a robot to cook and keep house. "http://anidb.net/ch138701 [Mina-chan]" is such a good housekeeper, Takuma jokes that she should become his wife. Mina takes Takuma's joke seriously, and slowly the two start doing more things together, like having a picnic outside. As time goes by, Takuma starts to fall for Mina, but can a human and a robot ever have an equal, loving relationship?
Source: Seven Seas Entertainment

AllTitles: Dungeon no Naka no Hito|Dungeon People|ダンジョンの中のひと
Description:
An unexplored dungeon, filled with monsters and traps. An expert thief, searching for her lost father. When http://anidb.net/ch138704 [Clay] delves into the dungeon deeper than any adventurer has ever gone, she is offered a job by the dungeon’s caretaker! Now, instead of exploring, Clay must learn how to interview new monsters, set traps and position slimes around the dungeon. Will this new career path bring her any closer to finding her father?
Source: Seven Seas Entertainment
